sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Flutter App
    participant BE as Cloud Run Backend
    participant GM as Gemini Live API

    App->>BE: POST /live/ephemeral-token
    BE-->>App: { token, model, tools }
    App->>GM: WebSocket connect
    App->>GM: setup { model, persona, tools }
    GM-->>App: setupComplete

    loop Voice Interaction
        App->>GM: realtimeInput { audio }
        GM-->>App: serverContent { audio }
        GM-->>App: toolCall { name, args }
        App->>BE: POST /live/tool-execute
        BE->>BE: Validate + Execute + Persist
        BE-->>App: { success, data }
        App->>GM: toolResponse { result }
    end

    App->>GM: close
